channel.title: How To Pack, Unpacked Files?
channel.description:

I Want To pack My Unpackedspawns.... I have Searched the Web For Hours, And Only Come across Afew, Which all they say is "delete packed, (run server/compile)"
This does not work For me? Am i Doing Something Wrong? I Also Noticed a Second "unpackedspawn" File, Do i delete it? :/
I Tried to Get Frost Dragons To Respawn, This is what i added Into Unpackedspawn.
[code]//frosts
51 1294 4497 -1, true 51 1287 4490 -1, true 51 1293 4490 -1, true 51 1294 4485 -1, true 51 1301 4487 -1, true 51 1297 4490 -1, true 51 1298 4496 -1, true 51 1305 4496 -1, true 51 1307 4491 -1, true 51 1315, 4487 -1, true 51 1318, 4494 -1, true 51 1314, 4493 -1, true 51 1326 4498 -1, true 51 1316 4502 -1, true 51 1298 4531, -1, true 51 1304, 4526 -1, true 51 1307 4534 -1, true 51 1312 4524, -1, true 51 1310 4518 -1, true 51 1319 4531 -1, true, 51 1325 4335 -1, true 51 1326 4527 -1, true 51 1323 4517 -1, true 51 1333, 4518 -1, true[/code]
